data.title: The Tat Talk
data.description: The Ink Head Society presents "The TatTalk". Welcome to the one and only greatest tattoo podcast! Our first series of episodes I will be discussing and sharing my opinion on the newest season of Ink Master: Return of the Masters. Every Tuesday starting January 9th at 10 PM Eastern, Spike will be airing new episodes of Ink Master. Then every Wednesday you the listeners will be receiving my thoughts and review on that episode. So get ready inkheads the first Ink Master podcast show is on its way!

data.title: The Middle of the Curve
data.description:
Welcome to the Middle of the Curve Podcast! We are a group of law school students here to discuss all things law school and post-grad. On our first episode, we discuss the first 1L semester, hand out some Book Awards for winter break characters, and set our goals for the next semester.

Please connect with us and share your experiences! Got questions about dating in law school, long-distance relationships, or want to share a cold call story of your own? Call in and leave a voicemail with only your first name and state plus your message at 321-895-4732. Follow us on Twitter at @middlecurve or DM us on Instagram at Middle_of_the_Curve.

Average guys for average folks. Law school is tough, but we’ll see you in the Middle of the Curve!
